      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VAINSTREAM (1) is racing in hot form, winning in a similar race to this on the Turf course here two back before a 2.6L defeat at Queanbeyan on Sunday. Martin's claim comes in handy and if he can slot in from the tricky draw, he'll be hard to hold out. MAGIC BERTIE (2) has disappointing form on paper, but this presents as a golden opportunity to get back to form. He's now with the Burleigh barn and comes right back in grade today. Can put his best foot forward. BEAU ROCK (3) resumed in a similar race and was solid despite being well beaten behind VAINSTREAM. Should be better for that effort and he won't be far away. OUR LADY ROCKSTAR (6) is another who comes through the same race and gets a weight swing in his favour. Drawn well and can be in the finish. YAEL'S DELIGHT (7) is better than she showed last time out and can improve.",
